<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Barefoot" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Barefoot,</orth> with naked feet: <cit><quote>I must dance b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 33</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 4, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.528" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 528</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.3.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 3, 39</bibl>.<lb />Adjectively: <cit><quote>lie tumbling in my b. way,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a b. brother,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 2, 4</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>